Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.28,0:01:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,THE INSIGNIA OF AVAN
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.13,0:01:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Begirama!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.68,0:02:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir Avan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.19,0:02:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Is everyone alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.19,0:02:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness.\NTalk about very nice timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.99,0:02:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.03,0:02:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't think he had the strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.29,0:02:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Master, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.08,0:02:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in a lot of pain.\NBut I don't have time for that now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.96,0:02:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,He's more powerful than\Nwhen he was the Dark Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.88,0:02:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only that, he has\Nthe Dark King backing him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.39,0:02:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Our enemy is far beyond my expectations.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.81,0:02:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,With our current strength...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.19,0:02:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,we can't win.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.65,0:02:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.57,0:02:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why he...\NHadlar, the Dark Commander...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.70,0:03:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,must be brought down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.49,0:03:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And Dai, Popp...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.29,0:03:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I ask that someday you two\Ndefeat Vearn, the Dark King!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.47,0:03:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I underestimated you.\NWell done, Avan, the Hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.68,0:03:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.43,0:03:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Master, do you intend to die?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.56,0:03:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Master, I'll fight with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.19,0:03:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Asutoron!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.27,0:03:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.57,0:03:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Asutoron!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.03,0:03:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Asutoron?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.49,0:03:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a high-level defensive spell
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.15,0:03:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,that turns the body to steel\Nand repels any magical attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.95,0:03:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But if we're like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.58,0:03:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.50,0:03:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You should all be safe now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.96,0:03:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You may watch my final battle from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.00,0:04:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,By "final," you mean...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.38,0:04:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do this! I'll fight!\NTogether with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.47,0:04:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,How foolish, Avan. To spend your remaining\NMagic Power on your students.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.28,0:04:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Those are...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.78,0:04:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Insignias of Avan!\NCertificates of graduation!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.74,0:04:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Graduation?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.12,0:04:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I give these to students\NI believe are fully trained.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.21,0:04:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai, you possess outstanding potential.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.42,0:04:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I regret our training was cut short\Nat three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.18,0:04:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,If we continued for the remaining four...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.26,0:04:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm certain you could have become a Hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.14,0:04:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Avan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.89,0:04:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That is why I give this to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.27,0:05:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Continue with your training\Nand become a true Hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.78,0:05:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Master, I...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.20,0:05:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.28,0:05:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.49,0:05:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do it, Master! I don't want that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.95,0:05:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop being so morbid!\NOur training isn't over yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.09,0:05:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.59,0:05:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care if you were the Hero once!\NWhy are you doing all this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.72,0:05:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You said yourself you can't beat him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.55,0:05:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because I can't beat him\Nthat I must risk my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.98,0:05:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, Popp,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.81,0:05:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe the power we gain through\Ntraining should be used to help others.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.86,0:05:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps my power was granted to me\Nby the gods to protect you on this day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.91,0:05:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do this, Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.16,0:05:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Someday I know you will understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.16,0:06:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So, hold onto this\Nfor when that day comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.42,0:06:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.42,0:06:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.67,0:06:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my. You haven't officially graduated\Nand you're already so emotional.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.39,0:06:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll need to work much, much harder\Nto become Heroes worthy of those.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.73,0:06:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Brass and Gomechan,\Nthank you for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.19,0:06:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir Avan, don't do anything rash!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.82,0:06:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I will not lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.46,0:06:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Done saying goodbye to your students?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.63,0:06:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us fight, Hadlar!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.38,0:06:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.76,0:06:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But having used your last Magic Power\Nto cast Asutoron has sealed your fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.34,0:06:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You've spent most of\Nyour Magic Power, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.24,0:07:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.00,0:07:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.84,0:07:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,As we stand...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.34,0:07:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,even with just combat skills...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.67,0:07:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I have more than enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.18,0:07:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,power to...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.89,0:07:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,tear you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.89,0:07:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,apart!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.57,0:07:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.69,0:07:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Move! Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.46,0:08:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Die, Avan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.52,0:08:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.61,0:08:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,A spell?! Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.65,0:08:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You should be out of Magic Power!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.61,0:08:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,This spell requires\Nvery little Magic Power.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.66,0:08:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead, it turns life energy\Ninto explosive power to defeat enemies!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.62,0:08:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! This spell is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.63,0:08:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! Don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.05,0:08:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll die! It'll kill you too, Avan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.05,0:08:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.23,0:09:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp, Dai! I leave the rest to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.40,0:09:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.36,0:09:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}Megante!{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.31,0:09:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.69,0:09:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir Avan used the spell Megante.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.98,0:09:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Megante?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.49,0:10:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,He used the final destructive spell\Nthat uses his own life to save his allies.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.58,0:10:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir Avan, you truly are...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.75,0:10:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Master used his own life to protect us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.54,0:10:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.09,0:10:18.55,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}BEGIRAMA{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}\NHEAT-TYPE SPELL
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.05,0:10:23.56,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}IONAZUN{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}\NEXPLOSION-TYPE SPELL
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.56,0:10:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that Master?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.15,0:10:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hadlar?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.99,0:10:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Where's Master?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.04,0:10:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You truly have grown weak, Avan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.97,0:11:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You used your own life to cast Megante,\Nand you still couldn't defeat me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.68,0:11:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Now there is nothing left to fear!\NThe Dark Army is unopposed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.65,0:11:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,He truly is a monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.36,0:11:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.40,0:11:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Curse you, Avan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.16,0:11:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to wipe out your students\Nhere and now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.71,0:11:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry! The effects of\NSir Avan's Asutoron still remain!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.47,0:11:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It will repel any attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.10,0:11:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be so sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.64,0:11:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Having you immobile is perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.48,0:11:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.48,0:11:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He can use Mera, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.65,0:12:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,My Mera is pure hellfire.\NIt will burn until my target is destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.57,0:12:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I simply cast it, and the moment your\NAsutoron wears off, you'll turn to ashes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.08,0:12:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't! Please don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.37,0:12:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You should be happy.\NWhen you die, you can go to the afterlife.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.63,0:12:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Your precious master is there,\Nwaiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.30,0:12:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's right! Master did it for us!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.14,0:12:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He gave his life so we could survive!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.35,0:12:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If we die here,\Nthen what did he sacrifice himself for?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.78,0:12:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have my life\Nbecause Master gave it to me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.05,0:13:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What?! Is he going to\Nbreak the Asutoron on his own?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.51,0:13:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is he?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.94,0:13:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,He broke the Asutoron!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.98,0:13:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You brat! Burn to death!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.24,0:13:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Merazoma!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.99,0:13:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Hyadain!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.00,0:13:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai used magic?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.75,0:13:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's stronger than mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.79,0:13:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,My flames...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.21,0:13:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll just pummel you to death!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.76,0:13:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.98,0:14:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this power?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.91,0:14:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible! Th-That crest...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.92,0:14:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,A Dragon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.38,0:14:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that light?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.97,0:14:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember!\NDai used powerful magic in battle before!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.93,0:14:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That mark appeared on his forehead then!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.69,0:14:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A Dragon Crest?!\NIs this boy a Dragon Knight?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.69,0:14:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Impossible!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.86,0:14:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.07,0:14:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you kill Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.95,0:14:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll pay for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.66,0:15:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get cocky, boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.43,0:15:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.01,0:15:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,This is impossible! I may have\Nsustained damage from Megante...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.73,0:15:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And he may be a student of Avan...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.85,0:15:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But how could I be overpowered\Nby a mere child?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.20,0:15:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.20,0:15:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Die! Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.75,0:15:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Eat this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.46,0:15:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}IORA!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.47,0:15:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.68,0:16:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,How's that? I used\Nthe last of my Magic Power on that spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.44,0:16:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Surely he's dead now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.23,0:16:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai! Don't tell me he killed you, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.28,0:16:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! There's no way I can lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.30,0:16:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.02,0:16:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't lose! Not to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.29,0:17:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.00,0:17:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai! Above you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.67,0:17:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Feel how powerful Master's attack is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.17,0:17:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,for yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.05,0:17:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.10,0:17:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}Avan...{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.18,0:17:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4&}Strash!{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.24,0:17:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Curse you, boy! I'll remember\Nthis humiliation and your name!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.62,0:17:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear I will kill you! Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.19,0:18:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai, are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.49,0:18:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Grampa, Gomechan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.62,0:18:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Hadlar?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.24,0:18:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, it seems he escaped.\NI saw him use a Chimaera Wing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.04,0:18:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.17,0:18:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.30,0:18:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.64,0:18:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.74,0:19:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The magic circle of light remains\Neven after Sir Avan has gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.16,0:19:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,He still protects us even now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.12,0:19:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you Master is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.08,0:19:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.67,0:19:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai, what will you do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.13,0:19:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.01,0:19:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you continue\Nyour magic training under me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.55,0:19:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Or...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.76,0:19:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.60,0:19:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Master gave me a mission.\NTo one day defeat Vearn, the Dark King.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.27,0:19:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.41,0:19:45.95,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,SOVEREIGN ROCK CASTLE
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.96,0:19:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see you took quite the beating, Hadlar.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.75,0:20:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me, my Dark King,\Nfor making you see me in this condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.84,0:20:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It matters not.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.39,0:20:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You have buried Avan, the Hero.\NConsider them wounds of honor.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.52,0:20:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,My Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.94,0:20:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have placed all of my trust in you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.73,0:20:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With your rival Avan dead,\Nno one can stop my Dark Army.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.20,0:20:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Go forth and fulfill your dream\Nof overthrowing the world.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.20,0:20:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Sire!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.58,0:20:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's true that Avan is dead.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.25,0:20:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But that boy Dai is a far greater threat.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.96,0:20:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wounded as I was, to overpower me,\NHadlar, the Dark Commander...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.76,0:20:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And that mark on his forehead.\NThe Dragon Crest.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.48,0:20:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If he really is a Dragon Knight...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.11,0:21:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And, with Avan's training,\Nif he manages to reach power of a Hero...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.36,0:21:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}he will become\Nfar more powerful than Avan!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.74,0:21:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The wounds I received from him\Nare proof of that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.21,0:21:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The wound from Dai heals slower\Nthan the wound from Avan.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.71,0:21:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In that instant,\NDai's blade surpassed that of his master!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.39,0:21:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I let him live, he is sure to grow into\Na terrifying enemy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.49,0:21:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I must crush him!\NWhile he still remains a fledgling!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.83,0:21:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,With my grand Dark Army!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.23,0:22:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kindness is the magic of kind people{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.23,0:22:25.99,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}yasashisa wa yasashii hito ga tsukaeru mahou{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.15,0:22:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then do I have no choice\NBut to just be a normal person?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.15,0:22:32.99,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}jaa boku wa tada no hito de iru shikanaino?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.16,0:22:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm not sure{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.16,0:22:36.21,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}doudarou{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.50,0:22:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if the place I call home may change{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.50,0:22:44.17,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kaeru basho wa ne kawatte yuku kedo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.34,0:22:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Listen to me, Mother{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.34,0:22:46.72,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}naa kaasan boku wa{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.88,0:22:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I will never change those I protect{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.88,0:22:52.85,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}mamoru hito wo kaetari shinai{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.31,0:22:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder what you'd say{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.31,0:22:57.52,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}anata wa nannte iukana{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.69,0:23:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At times I can be cowardly and small{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.69,0:23:01.73,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tokiyori yowaki de chippoke de{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.90,0:23:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What would you say to me\NAs I hesitate to even hesitate?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.90,0:23:08.20,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}mayou koto ni mo mayou boku ni nannte iukana{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.36,0:23:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Unlike the today that I sought{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.36,0:23:14.03,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}sagashite ita kyou to chigatte{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.20,0:23:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sure you'd laugh at my disappointment{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.20,0:23:19.33,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ochikonnde shimau boku wo warau no darou{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.85,0:23:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With new determination in their hearts,\NDai and Popp leave Dermline Island.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.31,0:23:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Their first stop\Nis the Dark Forest of Romos Kingdom.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.23,0:23:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dai and Popp meet the girl Maam.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.32,0:23:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The terrifying footsteps\Nof monsters approach.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.99,0:23:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Can Dai and his friends\Nsafely make it through the forest?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.03,0:23:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Next time on{\i0}\NDRAGON QUEST The Adventure of Dai{\i1},{\i0}
